content: <?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>  <reference anchor='I-D.zourzouvillys-bliss-ach-http-api'> <front> <title>Basic HTTP API interface for ACH</title>  <author initials='T' surname='Zourzouvillys' fullname='Theo Zourzouvillys'>     <organization /> </author>  <date month='March' day='8' year='2009' />  <abstract><t>This document defines a RESTful HTTP API that enables a SIP device (or agent activing on behalf of) a way to configure, enable, or disable services provided by the network.</t></abstract>  </front>  <seriesInfo name='Internet-Draft' value='draft-zourzouvillys-bliss-ach-http-api-01' /> <format type='TXT'         target='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zourzouvillys-bliss-ach-http-api-01.txt' /> </reference>
